{{- define "install.tldr" -}}
## TL;DR
```console
$ helm repo add {{ template "repository.organization" . }} {{ template "helm.url" . }}
$ helm repo update
$ helm install {{ template "chart.name" . }} {{ template "helm.path" . }}
```
